                "
            "
                <b>
                  <nobr>
                <div>
                  <b>
                    <nobr>
                      "This text is in a div inside a nobr"
                    "More text that should not be in the nobr, i.e., the
            nobr should have closed the div inside it implicitly. "
                  <pre>
                    "A pre tag outside everything else."
                  "
            
